Some people ask me, “Nebo, what means financial freedom?” Does that mean you have to have millions and millions of dollars?

No, financial freedom means finding happiness and finding a lifestyle you like. Something that makes you happy to live and to have things you want. Like a car. You don’t have to have a yacht. But something that is your dream and to live that life. So guys, find out what you like, where you need to be, where you need to live and invest in real estate. Real estate can help you achieve financial freedom. It did for me.
